    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family of birds containing ducks, geese, and swans. Various classifications divide it into 3 subfamilies and 8 to 12 tribes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
